## 2️⃣ SIGNUP - Register New User
**Method:** POST
**URL:**
```
http://localhost:5005/auth/signup
```

**Headers:**
```
Content-Type: application/json
```

**Body (JSON):**
```json
{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "Test123!"
}
```

**Expected Response (201):**
```json
{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "_id": "..."
}
```

**TIP:** Change the email/username for each new user!

---

## 3️⃣ LOGIN - Get JWT Token
**Method:** POST
**URL:**
```
http://localhost:5005/auth/login
```

**Headers:**
```
Content-Type: application/json
```

**Body (JSON):**
```json
{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}
```

**Expected Response (200):**
```json
{
  "authToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "message": "Login successful! Token valid for 6 hours"
}
```

**⚠️ COPY THE authToken - You need it for protected routes!**

---

## 4️⃣ VERIFY - Check Token Validity
**Method:** GET
**URL:**
```
http://localhost:5005/auth/verify
```

**Headers:**
```
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
```

**⚠️ Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login!**

**Format Example:**
```
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJfaWQiOiI2OGZhMGZlYTVlMjBiNzhhZWIxOTk0ZDciLCJpYXQiOjE2OTg3NjU0MzIsImV4cCI6MTY5ODc4NzAzMn0.abc123
```

**Body:** None

**Expected Response (200):**
```json
{
  "message": "Token is valid!",
  "user": {
    "_id": "...",
    "iat": 1698765432,
    "exp": 1698787032
  }
}
```

