## 🧪 TESTING WORKFLOW

### Quick Test Sequence:
1. ✅ Test server is running → GET /api
2. ✅ Signup a new user → POST /auth/signup
3. ✅ Login with that user → POST /auth/login (COPY TOKEN!)
4. ✅ Verify token works → GET /auth/verify (paste token)

### Error Testing:
5. ❌ Try login with wrong password → Should get 403
6. ❌ Try signup with duplicate email → Should get 403
7. ❌ Try verify without token → Should get 403
8. ❌ Try verify with invalid token → Should get 403

