## 🔍 STATUS CODES REFERENCE

| Code | Meaning | When You'll See It |
|------|---------|-------------------|
| 200 | OK | Successful login, verify |
| 201 | Created | Successful signup |
| 403 | Forbidden | Invalid credentials, no/invalid token |
| 500 | Server Error | Database issues, code errors |

---

## 🐛 COMMON ERRORS & FIXES

### "Invalid Credentials" (403)
- Wrong email or password on login
- Email already exists on signup
- **Fix:** Check credentials or use different email

### "No token found" (403)
- Missing Authorization header
- **Fix:** Add header: `Authorization: Bearer TOKEN`

### "Invalid Token" (403)
- Token expired (>6 hours old)
- Token malformed or corrupted
- Wrong TOKEN_SECRET in .env
- **Fix:** Login again to get fresh token

### "Cannot POST /auth/signup" (404)
- Server not running
- Wrong URL
- **Fix:** Check server is running on :5005

